---
/**
 * Testimonials section in a "bento" card grid style (4 cards).
 * Matches site styling: container-w, rounded-2xl, subtle borders, white cards.
 */
const { id, class: _class, className = "", title = "Testimoni Pengguna WithLia", ...rest } = Astro.props;
---

<section {...rest} id={id} class={`w-full py-20 ${_class ? _class : ""} ${className}`}>
  <div class="container-w">
    <h2 class="text-center font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-3xl md:text-3xl">
      {title}
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:mt-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <article class="md:col-span-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-card">
        <header class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[var(--blue)]/10 text-[var(--blue)] font-bold">A</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Adit</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-black/60">Owner UMKM F&B</div>
          </div>
        </header>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-black/80">
          “Konten jadi 3× lebih cepat, dan engagement naik 45% di minggu ke-2. Framework-nya jelas, tinggal eksekusi.”
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 2 (Bank Raya Indonesia) -->
      <article class="md:col-span-7 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-card">
        <header class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[var(--orange)]/10 text-[var(--orange)] font-bold">BR</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Robby,Software Development</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-black/60">Bank Raya Indonesia</div>
          </div>
        </header>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-black/80">
          “Materi dan framework WithLia sudah kami gunakan dalam presentasi Eksplorasi digital marketing di Bank Raya Indonesia.
          Sangat insightful dan mudah di implemantasikan sesuai dengan kebutuhan industri digital.
          Ini bukti bahwa materi dan AI assistant yang digunakan oleh WithLia sesuai dengan kebutuhan perusahaan.”
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <article class="md:col-span-7 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-card">
        <header class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-600 font-bold">B</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Bima</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-black/60">Owner Brand Fashion</div>
          </div>
        </header>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-black/80">
          “AI-nya paham tone brand. Caption dan ide konten nggak terasa generik, lebih nyambung ke audiensku.”
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <article class="md:col-span-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-card">
        <header class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-600 font-bold">D</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Dian</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-black/60">Edupreneur</div>
          </div>
        </header>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-black/80">
          “Mentornya responsif dan praktis. Roadmap 7 hari bikin aku beneran jalan — bukan cuma belajar.”
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</section>
